#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/glibc.xml:180
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The <emphasis>nss/tst-nss-files-hosts-multi</emphasis> test may fail for "
